      "title": "Notification issued by Central Bank Governor",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Governor of the Central Bank of Sri Lanka, Kalanidhi Nandalal Weerasinghe said that he can announce that there has been good progress in the negotiations with the International Monetary Fund.",
        "He also expressed hope that the first milestone of a staff-level agreement with the IMF could be reached soon."
